{
  "stem": "27335.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fir-- our first job was to go to a Polish farm, and there was already cultivating about 120-- 20 acres.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our first job was planting potatoes for that farmer, and my-- my little sister-- well, then she was-- she was hired by the same-- same farmer as a domestic girl.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there was only the mother and two-- two brothers around that farm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was our first job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1930.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1930, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We arrived in Edmonton, 1st of May.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were put in-- well, they had these-- these immigrants depots, at the time, in Winnipeg and in centers like Edmonton, and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there we just stayed there for a day and a night, and then they packed us in the car and drove us out to the place-- well, this is where you're going to live.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my-- my-- well, as I said, we had two breadwinners, my father and-- and-- and myself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and our first job, when we built up-- we, well, we put up with another family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we built a two-room house, half of-- of that family, half of the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they-- they had four children, all under the age of six.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, our family, well I was obviously-- I was, uh, just past 16.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My-- my sister was old enough to-- to-- to take a job as a domestic on-- on-- the farm there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was our first job, to work on the farm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we waited-- the biggest job in the place like that then was the harvest time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When came harvest time, then this-- uh, uh, Swartz, he was the-- the-- the settler there-- there, he-- he gave-- he gave us his address in Calgary-- he lived in Calgary.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
